{"tid":379584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人之前做過一個車費貴唔貴既訪問","createTime":"2017-08-29T12:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:20:22.000Z","uid":62784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb2a60ad9698e150137df5b032decd586695743","tid":379584,"uid":62784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"本身一有訪問電話<br />\n我就會cut線<br />\n但好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就幫左佢做呢個訪問<br />\n估唔到呢個係惡夢既開始<br />\n呢個月隔幾日打黎<br />\n叫我去拎返個禮品 <br />\n我連禮品都懶得去拎 <br />\n次次都cut線就算<br />\n今日仲癲到 有條友打黎話多謝我做訪問<br />\n然後一路話自己車費好貴 講自己好可憐<br />\n仲叫我得閒搵佢吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e2db45a06581efa694a7bb14368670a2e8a84b","tid":379584,"uid":24632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"之前問佢哋<br />\n<br />\n我：究竟咩研究咁犀利由我中學訪問到而家我出黎做嘢都仲未完，你地邊間公司？<br />\n西裝狗：實X （X德）<br />\n我：咪即係倫敦金<br />\n西裝狗：都係環球貴金屬姐<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就走左"}]}